snippet.title: RoboDunk Reveal Trailer - Roguelite Basketball Combat for PC & consoles
snippet.description:
ROBODUNK is NBA Jam meets Rogue Legacy, with robots. 
⇨⇨ https://steam.robodunk.com ⇦⇦
Massive dunks, satisfying tackles and explosive weapons. Replayable campaign where every match is different, and you can buy the next permanent upgrade even if you die. JUST...ONE...MORE...DUNK!

WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1557720
WEBSITE: https://robodunk.com
DISCORD: https://discord.robodunk.com

ORIGINAL ROBOT DESIGNS:
MittenNinja (https://www.flickr.com/photos/mittenninja/)
A. YATES (https://www.flickr.com/photos/ekil)
Aardvark17 (https://www.flickr.com/photos/aardvark17/)
KungFujiApple (https://www.flickr.com/photos/153291692@N06/)
the sylince (https://www.flickr.com/photos/188298872@N07/)
Omniscient Frog (https://www.flickr.com/photos/141290049@N07/)
Chubbybots (https://www.youtube.com/user/chubbybots)
Jay Biquadrate (https://www.flickr.com/photos/58283021@N03/)
